2019-10-18 HWV

In this folder, the code is developed for designing multiple NupY designs.

These designs are created using the average composition of GLFG-Nups, considering the collapsed and extended domain. Original FG repeats or GLFG repeats are excluded.

The code accounts for the native FG:GLFG density.

As an update to the code, we also included checks for accidental FGs.
We created 10 different designs (disordered acc. to PONDR), which are then further optimized using DISOPRED.

Then, the genes are determined.

